renowned Rockpool Restaurant have
worked together to provide menus
reflecting the Spirit
of Australia.
Quality seasonal
produce is sourced to
create dishes that capture
diverse flavours and
regional inspirations.
Your Flight Attendants
are happy to assist you in your
selection or suggest an alternative if
your choice is not available.
